title: Ticket, passport and tarot cards. Episode 18. The Star
brief_description: AIRED 29 December 2005 Based on a popular book from Tarot expert Linda Marson, this series is a a unique combination of personal diary, travel journal and Tarot imagery. Screened as a weekly show on Channel 31 in Melbourne, T, P and TC was a five minute filler program that screened from 1 September 2005 - 26 January 2006.
